      "location": "Marriott, Platinum Ballroom 3 & 4",
      "description": "As the women’s health market continues to grow and diversify product offerings, “the Queen of Ayurvedic herbs,” shatavari is poised to gain significant traction with Nutritional Business Journal projecting growth rates upward of 38% over the next four years. Helping to drive this growth is breakthrough branded ingredient SRI-81 Shatavari. Backed by years of research, SRI-81 has been clinically proven to offer a holistic intervention that supports through every phase of a women’s life. In this session, led by renowned physician, educator and holistic medicine expert Dr. Low Dog, learn the rich traditional heritage and emerging clinical science of Shatavari, along with insights into how SRI-81 can serve as a foundation for innovation across multiple women’s wellness categories.",
