      "description": "The MAHA movement has ignited passionate debate across the health and food world. But what if, instead of taking sides, we stepped into curiosity together? Join The Fifth Field’s Carlotta Mast and Kate LaBrosse for a 90-minute facilitated dialogue designed to move our community from polarization to possibility. Explore your own assumptions, uncover common ground, and experience how story and culture can renew our collective imagination of health. Leave with tools to host courageous conversations in your own organization and communities that unite people and teams around purposeful action in the pursuit of accessible health and wellbeing for all people. When we listen to understand, we remember: we're on the same side of health.",
