      "endIso": "2026-03-06T00:00:00.000Z",
      "timeLabel": "3:00 PM - 4:00 PM",
      "location": "Marriott, Grand Ballroom E",
      "description": "By 2030 over 30 million Americans may interact with a GLP-1 agonist medication as a tool for weight loss, blood sugar, inflammation, cognitive health and more. It's already having a ripple effect on consumer health, healthcare, food and ingredient industries. But the BIGGER story? These medications are introducing everyone to weight-health hormones. That these hormones regulate weight and health. That to enjoy weight health, today and tomorrow, a person needs to optimize their weight-health hormones... and the number of Americans that this impacts? 9 out of 10! What does this mean for the food, supplement, healthcare industries and the media? This session will provide insights, strategies, and guardrails for navigating weight health in the era of GLP-1. *Following the presentation, Ashley will do a book signing! Bring your own copy to be signed - plus, the first 20 people in line to attend this session will receive a free copy of YOUR BEST SHOT .",
